OASISFormat: 0.4
Name:        sociaml-vcard
Version:     0.2.1
Synopsis:    vCard library for OCaml
Description:
  Library for parsing and creating contact information in the vCard format.
  Currently only version 4.0 of the vCard specification is supported.
Authors:     Dominic Price
